# Bus Tracker SG

Personal bus arrival tracker for stops B20019 (Home) and B18101 (Office).
Buses tracked: 97, 97E, 197, 963.

## Deploy to Vercel

### One-time setup

1. Install Node.js from https://nodejs.org (LTS version)
2. Install Vercel CLI:
   ```
   npm install -g vercel
   ```
3. Create a free account at https://vercel.com

### Deploy

Open a terminal in this folder and run:

```
vercel
```

- When asked "Set up and deploy?" → Y
- Project name → press Enter (accept default)
- Which directory → press Enter (current folder)
- Override settings? → N

Vercel will give you a live URL like:
  https://bus-app-xxx.vercel.app

Bookmark that on your phone — done.

### Redeploy after any changes

```
vercel --prod
```

## File structure

```
bus-app/
├── index.html     — frontend UI
├── api/
│   └── bus.js     — serverless proxy to LTA DataMall API
└── vercel.json    — routing config
```

## Notes

- Auto-refreshes every 30 seconds
- Load indicator dots: 🟢 Seats Available / 🟡 Standing / 🔴 Limited Standing
- LTA API key is hardcoded in api/bus.js
